---
// VibeCodingPipeline.astro — Interactive CI/CD pipeline showing where to catch AI-generated vulns
---

<div class="vcp-wrap">
  <h3 class="vcp-title">🔍 Where to Catch AI-Generated Bugs</h3>
  <p class="vcp-sub">The earlier you catch it, the cheaper it is to fix. Hover each stage.</p>

  <div class="vcp-pipeline">
    <div class="vcp-stage vcp-stage--1" tabindex="0">
      <div class="vcp-icon">✍️</div>
      <div class="vcp-name">IDE</div>
      <div class="vcp-detail">
        <strong>Pre-commit hooks</strong>
        <p>Semgrep rules catch SQLi, XSS, path traversal the moment the AI generates them. Zero cost to fix.</p>
        <span class="vcp-catch">Catches: 60% of vulns</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="vcp-connector"><div class="vcp-arrow"></div></div>

    <div class="vcp-stage vcp-stage--2" tabindex="0">
      <div class="vcp-icon">📦</div>
      <div class="vcp-name">PR Review</div>
      <div class="vcp-detail">
        <strong>AI-aware code review</strong>
        <p>Flag "vibe-coded" patterns: missing input validation, no error handling, inline secrets.</p>
        <span class="vcp-catch">Catches: 25% of vulns</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="vcp-connector"><div class="vcp-arrow"></div></div>

    <div class="vcp-stage vcp-stage--3" tabindex="0">
      <div class="vcp-icon">🧪</div>
      <div class="vcp-name">CI Pipeline</div>
      <div class="vcp-detail">
        <strong>SAST + Secret Scanning</strong>
        <p>Full static analysis (CodeQL, Snyk) on every push. Blocks merge if critical findings exist.</p>
        <span class="vcp-catch">Catches: 12% of vulns</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="vcp-connector"><div class="vcp-arrow"></div></div>

    <div class="vcp-stage vcp-stage--4" tabindex="0">
      <div class="vcp-icon">🚨</div>
      <div class="vcp-name">Production</div>
      <div class="vcp-detail">
        <strong>WAF + Runtime Protection</strong>
        <p>Last resort. RASP blocks exploitation but the bug is already deployed. Expensive to remediate.</p>
        <span class="vcp-catch">Catches: 3% — too late</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .vcp-wrap {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0c1220 0%, #1e1b2e 100%);
    border-radius: 1rem; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0;
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2);
  }
  .vcp-title { color: #f1f5f9; font-size: 1.25rem; margin: 0 0 0.25rem; }
  .vcp-sub { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.875rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }
  .vcp-pipeline { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0; overflow-x: auto; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .vcp-pipeline { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; } .vcp-connector { display: none; } }
  .vcp-stage {
    flex: 1; min-width: 120px; text-align: center; cursor: pointer;
    padding: 1rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 0.75rem; transition: all 0.3s;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
  }
  .vcp-stage:hover, .vcp-stage:focus { background: rgba(99,102,241,0.08); border-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.3); }
  .vcp-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .vcp-name { color: #e2e8f0; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .vcp-detail {
    max-height: 0; overflow: hidden; transition: max-height 0.4s ease;
    text-align: left; padding: 0 0.5rem;
  }
  .vcp-stage:hover .vcp-detail, .vcp-stage:focus .vcp-detail { max-height: 200px; }
  .vcp-detail strong { color: #a5b4fc; font-size: 0.75rem; }
  .vcp-detail p { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.7rem; margin: 0.25rem 0; line-height: 1.4; }
  .vcp-catch { display: inline-block; margin-top: 0.25rem; font-size: 0.65rem; color: #34d399; font-weight: 600; }
  .vcp-connector { display: flex; align-items: center; padding-top: 1.5rem; }
  .vcp-arrow { width: 20px; height: 2px; background: rgba(99,102,241,0.4); position: relative; }
  .vcp-arrow::after { content: '→'; position: absolute; right: -8px; top: -8px; color: rgba(99,102,241,0.6); font-size: 0.75rem; }
</style>
